This is the EES4100 Bridge Project and is used to establish a connection between the Modbus server and relay those details onto the BACnet client.

After building this application. It can be run by locating the ./EES4100_Testbench/src/ directory and typing './bacnet_server' into the terminal window.

Details are as follows:

BACnet Side 				Modbus Side
Device 120 At Instance 0		Register 120
Device 120 At Instance 1		Register 121
Device 120 At Instance 2		Register 122
Device 120 At Instance 3		Register 123

